      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay that makes sense. so if i start paying extra every month, it should definitely help. but it still feels like these hidden costs are just designed to keep me in debt forever. is there anything else i should watch out for that might be working against me behind the scenes?",
      "source": "evaluator"
